# ── Helius — Solana RPC + DAS API ────────────────────────────────────────────
# Best-in-class Solana data: mint/freeze authority, token metadata, NFTs.
# Required for Solana scam detection.
# https://dev.helius.xyz → Create API Key
HELIUS_API_KEY=d8893121-a7b0-43a6-93e1-bfcb71d0cc27


# ── Block Explorer API Keys ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used by scam detection to check contract verification and source code.
# All are optional — missing keys = fewer scam signals, not broken.
# Most offer a free tier sufficient for DappScore's usage.
#
# Chains using public Blockscout (no key needed):
#   Zora, Unichain, ZetaChain, HyperEVM, Monad, SEI

